
**Policy Name:** parkmycloud-permissions

**Policy Description:** The minimum permissions required to run ParkMyCloud:


{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Action": [
                "iam:GetUser",
                "ec2:Describe*",
                "ec2:StartInstances",
                "ec2:StopInstances",
                "autoscaling:Describe*",
                "autoscaling:UpdateAutoScalingGroup"
            ],
            "Resource": [
                "*"
            ],
            "Effect": "Allow"
        }
    ]
}
